Maxis Communications Logo Maxis Communications or Maxis Berhad is a communications service provider in Malaysia. Headquartered in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia, providing a variety of communication products, applications and value added services for consumers, large enterprises and small & medium business owners. Maxis uses the dialing prefixes of “011 12000000 through 12499999”, “012”, “014-2”, and “017”. The majority of the company’s stake is owned by billionaire Ananda Krishnan. Source
